  "diagram_type": "stateDiagram",
  "code": "%%{HealthTech_PatientRecords}}}%%\n\nstateDiagram-v2\ntitle: SM-08.01 — Ethics Evaluation Flow (HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)\n\n[HealthTech_EMR_Sync] --> PENDING : AlignmentChecked (HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)\nnote right of PENDING\n  Ethics evaluation initiated  \n  • triggered by new PoC or Proposal event  \n  • fetch rubric and Manifesto version  \n  • assign evaluator (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\nend note\n\nPENDING --> EVALUATING : EvaluationStarted\nnote right of EVALUATING\n  Process input through multi-layer rubric:  \n  • quantitative: resonance, alignment  \n  • qualitative: intent, externalities  \n  • hybrid AI-human scoring possible\nend note\n\nEVALUATING --> UNDER_REVIEW : ScoreComputed / RequiresHumanReview\nnote right of UNDER_REVIEW\n  If confidence < threshold, escalate  \n  • peer review or ethics board confirmation  \n  • discussion / comments appended  \nend note\n\nEVALUATING --> APPROVED : EthicsPassed (HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine)\nEVALUATING --> REJECTED : EthicsFailed (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)\n\nUNDER_REVIEW --> APPROVED : Confirmed / ConsensusReached\nUNDER_REVIEW --> REJECTED : EthicsViolationConfirmed\n\nAPPROVED --> ATTESTATION : AttestationIssued (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)\nnote right of ATTESTATION\n  Issue ethics attestation (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)  \n  • stored in PoCI (HealthTech_PatientRecords)  \n  • feeds resonance scoring (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)  \n  • updates metrics (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)\nend note\n\nATTESTATION --> [HealthTech_PatientRecords] : EvaluationClosed\n\nREJECTED --> FLAGGED : FlaggedForViolation\nFLAGGED --> GOV_NOTIFY : GovernanceAlertRaised (HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine)\nGOV_NOTIFY --> [HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault] : EthicsCaseLogged\n\n%% ---- Exceptional paths ----\nPENDING --> FAILED : InvalidInput / RubricMissing\nEVALUATING --> FAILED : ModelError / Timeout\nFAILED --> [HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault] : EvaluationAborted\n\n%% ===== Styling =====\nclassDef core fill:#ff8b00,stroke:#333,color:#fff,font-weight:bold;\nclass PENDING,EVALUATING,UNDER_REVIEW,APPROVED,REJECTED,ATTESTATION,FLAGGED,GOV_NOTIFY,FAILED core;",
