        "AlignmentChecked",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以起点是EMR_Sync，然后进入PENDING状态。这个PENDING状态需要包含哪些信息？比如评估器的分配逻辑？",
      "elements_involved": [
