    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，PENDING状态要记录三点：触发来源、获取的Manifesto版本，以及指定的评估器。评估器就是从EMR_Sync分配的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PENDING",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "AlignmentChecked"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把PENDING状态及其注释加上。接下来从PENDING应该流转到哪个状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PENDING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
